name: XYZ
description: GIF series from 2012 which tried to make several choreographies with the gizmo, this one is the more simple and confusing. Its optical effect reminds me of / The Spinning Dancer - 'Some observers initially see the figure as spinning clockwise and some counterclockwise. Additionally, some may see the figure suddenly spin in the opposite direction. The illusion derives from an inherent ambiguity from the lack of visual cues for depth.'
